tellina della fine del VI-inizio V sec. a.C. trova riscontro nel Nannelaios o meglio Nanelaios di una nota defixio selinuntina'. (Entella inscr. is Nenci, Novita..., in Atti delle Seconde Gionate...elima, 1994.-->\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>56.1100\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>50.1023\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>45.1415\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"BE\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>1998.0607\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/77P5MNIR\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001282\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGDS2\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Dubois\u003